10#include "output.h"
11
12int test_printf_stdout(const char *fmt, ...)
13{
14 va_list ap;
15 int ret;
16
17 va_start(ap, fmt);
18 ret = test_vprintf_stdout(fmt, ap);
19 va_end(ap);
20
21 return ret;
22}
23
24int test_printf_stderr(const char *fmt, ...)
25{
26 va_list ap;
27 int ret;
28
29 va_start(ap, fmt);
30 ret = test_vprintf_stderr(fmt, ap);
31 va_end(ap);
32
33 return ret;
34}
